OL,3,CMan jailed over antisemitic messages
OL,4,Cto MP
OL,6,FA man who sent a barrage of
OL,7,Fantisemitic messages to a Jewish MP
OL,8,Fwhile drunk has been jailed.
OL,10,FKevin Smith was sentenced to eight
OL,11,Fweeks on Thursday after admitting to
OL,12,Fthe string of voice messages and 300
OL,13,Ftexts to Alex Sobel, the Labour MP for
OL,14,FLeeds Central and Headingley, in March
OL,15,Flast year.
