OL,6,FWhile the voice messages were
OL,7,Fdescribed as "generally unpleasant and
OL,8,Foffensive", texts sent to Mr Sobel
OL,9,Fwere directly antisemitic, Leeds
OL,10,FMagistrate's Court heard, and included
OL,11,Fphrases like "kill the Jews" and "they
OL,12,Fshould be arrested for war crimes".
OL,14,FThe 61-year-old, who told arresting
OL,15,Fofficers he was exercising his right
OL,16,Fto free speech, looked confused as he
OL,17,Fwas led from the dock, saying "I don't
OL,18,Fbelieve this".
