OL,6,FDespite his claims of being under the
OL,7,Finfluence at the time of sending the
OL,8,Fmessages, district judge David Kitson
OL,9,Ftold him he had shown no remorse,
OL,10,Freferencing the assassination of Mr
OL,11,FSobel's former colleague Jo Cox in
OL,12,F2016.
OL,14,FThe judge told him: "Whilst we all
OL,15,Fenjoy freedom of speech in this
OL,16,Fcountry, it is a qualified right."
OL,18,F"The targeting of people because of
OL,19,Ftheir religion is simply not
OL,20,Fpermissible.
