OL,6,F"Where an MP is targeted that must
OL,7,Fmean, in my judgment, high culpability.
OL,9,F"By targeting an MP, that undermines
OL,10,Fthe democratic process and democratic
OL,11,Finstitutions in this country."
OL,13,FJudge Kitson added: "We are all aware
OL,14,Fthat in recent times, sadly, at least
OL,15,Ftwo Members of Parliament have lost
OL,16,Ftheir lives after being targeted by
OL,17,Ffanatical individuals ` one very close
OL,18,Fto this particular area."
