OL,6,FJo Cox, the late Labour MP for Batley
OL,7,Fand Spen, was shot and stabbed by far-
OL,8,Fright fanatic Thomas Mair while
OL,9,Fattending a surgery for constituents
OL,10,Fin Birstall in June 2016.
OL,12,FSmith's messages had left Mr Sobel
OL,13,Ffeeling concerned for his family's
OL,14,Fsafety, the court heard.
OL,16,FA pre-sentecing report had also said
OL,17,FSmith "didn't care about the impact on
OL,18,FMr Sobel as he doesn't know him and he
OL,19,Fdislikes MPs in general".
