OL,6,FMr Sobel said after the hearing: "I
OL,7,Fwould like to thank West Yorkshire
OL,8,FPolice for their work on this case and
OL,9,Ffor the support they have shown to me
OL,10,Fand my team.
OL,12,F"I hope Mr Smith is able to move
OL,13,Fforward with his life, make positive
OL,14,Fchanges, and access the support he
OL,15,Fneeds to do so."
